text: Willow Brook is an unincorporated community in Buchanan County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Willow Brook was established in 1878, and remained in operation until 1911. The community was named for the willow timber along a nearby creek. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Buchanan County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Willow Brook, Missouri
